<li><cite class="citation book"><a href="/wiki/Martha_Young-Scholten" title="Martha Young-Scholten">Young-Scholten, M.</a> (2002). "Orthographic input in L2 phonological development".  In Burmeister, P.; Piske, T.; Rohde, A. <i>An integrated View of Language Development: Papers in Honor of Henning Wode</i>. Trier: Wissenschaftlicher Verlag Trier. pp.&#160;263–279.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=Orthographic+input+in+L2+phonological+development&amp;rft.btitle=An+integrated+View+of+Language+Development%3A+Papers+in+Honor+of+Henning+Wode&amp;rft.place=Trier&amp;rft.pages=263-279&amp;rft.pub=Wissenschaftlicher+Verlag+Trier&amp;rft.date=2002&amp;rft.aulast=Young-Scholten&amp;rft.aufirst=M.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACritical+period+hypothesis" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r886058088"/></li></ul>
